The paper deals with online learning algorithms for regression, which is a topic that falls under the machine learning and artificial intelligence subfields of computer science. The paper also specifically addresses non-stationary environments, which is a common problem in systems and control theory (cs.SY) and time series analysis (cs.ST). The use of linear functions and analysis of regret also suggests a focus on optimization and algorithms (cs.DS). Overall, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.ST (Statistics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
